description: Forest Department - Order to declare - the State Lands in Mundalama Lagoon, Mundalama D/S Division, Puttalam District as Kattakaduwa Mangalaeliya Reserved Forest and the Ettalapitiya Forest in Bandarawela D/S Division, the Pahamburutota Forest in Haliela D/S Division of Badulla District; the Pitaneluwayaya alias Galwetiyaya Forest, the Potawa Natural Forest and the Walmoruwa Radawana Forest in Naula D/S Division, Matale District as Reserved Forests
